headline: Spotting Winners: Wabtec (NYSE:WAB) And Heavy Transportation Equipment Stocks In Q4
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how heavy transportation equipment stocks fared in Q4, starting with Wabtec (NYSE:WAB).
